  "title": "Caesr: Automate Content Research and Drafting with One Prompt",
  "excerpt": "Automate content research and drafting with Caesr. One prompt reads LinkedIn posts, summarizes insights, and writes a draft instantly.",
  "content": "<h2 id=\">Research Smarter, Write Faster with Caesr</h2>\n\n<p id=\">Caesr is our new natural language automation chat. </p><p id=\">Caesr handles all the work by taking your own descriptions of requirements to create your content instead of requiring you to manually browse posts and note down information before drafting your content.<br>And yes, Caesr works across multiple languages, so your research and writing can happen in any language you’re most comfortable with.</p><h2 id=\"><strong id=\">Turning Research into Action</strong><br></h2>\n\n<p id=\">Caesr can open websites, capture recent posts, summarize key insights, check trending hashtags, and produce a perfect draft with one request.</p><p id=\">The process which required multiple hours of monotonous work now performs in a unified stream.</p><h2 id=\"><strong id=\">How the Demo Unfolds</strong></h2>\n\n<p id=\">Here is the full prompt i used this demos:</p>\n\n<div data-rt-embed-type='true'><blockquote style=\"margin:16px 0;padding:12px 16px;background:#f5f5f5; border-left:4px solid #d0d0d0;border-radius:8px;font-family:ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,monospace;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6; color:#111;\"> “I need you to perform a complete social media intelligence and content drafting task from scratch. Adapt the tone of a confident and forward-thinking tech innovator for the final output. First, open a web browser. In separate tabs, navigate to the following LinkedIn URLs, read the three most recent posts, summarize the key themes, check trending hashtags, and draft a professional update in that tone.” </blockquote></div><p id=\">Caesr executed the instructions step by step:</p>\n\n<ol start=\"1\" id=\"><li id=\"><strong id=\">Open multiple tabs</strong> - navigated directly to the requested LinkedIn pages.</li><li id=\"><strong id=\">Collected insights</strong> – read the three most recent posts from each page.</li><li id=\"><strong id=\">Summarized the key message</strong> – extracted the core theme from every post.</li><li id=\"><strong id=\">Checked hashtag trends </strong>- reviewed hashtag trends to find out which hashtags were trending at that time.</li><li id=\"><strong id=\">Generated a draft of the post</strong> - created professional LinkedIn post in the desired style.</li></ol><div data-rt-embed-type='true'><iframe src=\"https://www.loom.com/embed/00f4e95986b846bda4e5ccc3856d44dc\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen style=\"width:100%; height:500px; border-radius:12px;\"></iframe></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"><strong id=\">Why This Use Case Stands Out</strong></h2>\n\n<p id=\">The demo shows that Caesr carries out responsibilities which go past standard task completion</p>\n\n<ul id=\"><li id=\">End-to- end flow - from raw research to completed the draft with one go.</li><li id=\">Insight generation - make insights by uniting various posts into a unified story.</li><li id=\">Tone flexibility - apply writing style what u want, from professional to casual.</li><li id=\">Reusable method - use the same prompt style for blogs, newsletters, or internal briefs.</li></ul><h2 id=\"><strong id=\">Ready for the Next Chapter</strong></h2>\n\n<p id=\">Researching and creating the drafts are just a start. The natural language approach functions to <a href=\"https://www.askui.com/blog-posts/caesr-automate-shopping-with-a-single-prompt\" id=\">simplify shopping operations</a> as well as<a href=\"https://www.askui.com/blog-posts/automate-invoice-to-excel-with-one-prompt\" id=\"> invoice management</a> and scheduling processes.</p>\n\n<div data-rt-embed-type='true'><style> .interactive-cta { transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; } .interactive-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); } </style> <div class=\"interactive-cta\" style=\" margin:40px 0; padding:36px; background:#f7f7f8; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; \"> <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; margin:0; font-family:Inter, Arial, sans-serif; color:#111;\"> ✨ Step into the future of automation on September 30.<br> <span style=\"color:#4F46E5; font-weight:500;\">Experience Caesr for yourself.</span> </p> </div></div>",
